UniGo Map Advanced Pack (Leaflet / React-Leaflet) — ORIGINAL
Generated: 2026-03-02T15:53:31.294547Z

This pack complements the previous controls pack and adds the OTHER map features I mentioned:
1) Snap-to-road (OSRM Map Matching) helper
2) Driver smoothing (GPS jitter filter) hook
3) Follow mode (camera behavior) controller hook
4) Route progress line (completed vs remaining) component
5) Auto reroute (detect deviation + refresh route) hook

No third-party code copied. You may need to set:
- VITE_OSRM_BASE_URL (e.g. https://your-osrm-host)
Optionally:
- VITE_OSRM_PROFILE (default 'driving')

Apply steps: docs/APPLY_ADVANCED_MAP.md